From 3e321f06ca1ae59dd2e029690dc54f69189cf6a3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Rakshitha SK <rsk@marvell.com>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 08:46:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] sonic-yang-models-Add-YANG-model-for-OSPFv2 Problem: OSPFv2
 CONFIG_DB tables had no YANG model. config apply-patch reported "no YANG
 models" for all OSPFV2_* tables and skipped validation.

RCA:
sonic-ospfv2.yang was missing. Without it, sonic-yang and CVL could
not validate OSPF field types, ranges, and enum values.

Fix:

Add sonic-ospfv2.yang to yang-models/
Register in setup.py package_data
Add OSPF entries to sample_config_db.json
Add YANG validation test cases (tests/yang_model_tests/)

Signed-off-by: Rakshitha SK <rsk@marvell.com>
---
 src/sonic-yang-models/setup.py                |   1 +
 .../tests/files/sample_config_db.json         |  40 +
 .../tests/yang_model_tests/tests/ospfv2.json  |  96 +++
 .../yang_model_tests/tests_config/ospfv2.json | 573 +++++++++++++
 .../yang-models/sonic-ospfv2.yang             | 799 ++++++++++++++++++
 5 files changed, 1509 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 src/sonic-yang-models/tests/yang_model_tests/tests/ospfv2.json
 create mode 100644 src/sonic-yang-models/tests/yang_model_tests/tests_config/ospfv2.json
 create mode 100644 src/sonic-yang-models/yang-models/sonic-ospfv2.yang

